data.description: COUNTRY ROADS, TAKE ME HOME to this charming 4 bed, 2 bath farmhouse on 15 acres of picturesque Hillsdale County countryside. Includes a spacious 40x60 barn with 2+stalls, electric & water. Perfect for horses or livestock. Five acres of pasture area available for grazing plus 10 tillable acres.  There are several fruit producing trees on the property and nice level area for your seasonal vegetable garden. Enjoy the tranquility of this rural setting. Schedule your personal tour today!
